解個個都話要除鞋先上機？ 係因為去日本所以和風？ 即係地板係榻榻米？"},{"pid":"e4eece4e8a0a321cabf4678c022483b362d95ed3","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個乘客要帶一樣食物上機<br />\n好似開大食會咁share黎食<br />\n無帶係唔可以食其他人既食物<br />\n上次飛一轉美國 盤菠蘿腸仔勁受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM記得唔得，無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3306bb0f813d60a63d1d7f437c9dc1ab1cb2ea8","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果成功land到，記得一定要大大力拍手，如果無拍，回程機唔知你land唔land到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇背後原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a4eddb8239a830ea038cd2bdfe8d77bd7c332b","tid":385792,"uid":140241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:18:21.000Z","msg":"唔好怕醜，上機換鞋著拖鞋會舒服 d"},{"pid":"386b0229c667bf8345b0a6e8905b96e89c2cafa4","tid":385792,"uid":106018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一 定 要 叫 杯 麵 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛機杯麵係咪貴啲？</blockquote><br />\n睇錯左 飛機杯 麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa119a8f4ae6ea2b070ec50665e1b3f6f76ceaf","tid":385792,"uid":79021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"記得帶回鄉證。"},{"pid":"1dee221706ff80b9469c22504550129b140d95e5","tid":385792,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"聽到brace就歡呼"},{"pid":"3e3b8b5547f97b302070296d33c35e6980c9f011","tid":385792,"uid":82764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"坐穩d"},{"pid":"5c58b0a360bcedc6eb9e6259c9f06c4011085119","tid":385792,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"一上機就去機頭 問可唔可以參觀駕駛倉<br />\n見到空姐一定要打招呼<br />\n一上機要去廁所洗手先 唔係會唔比你坐"},{"pid":"b03063b079c84746dcd03fd6f3dc42bb9da18fa3","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一上機就去機頭 問可唔可以參觀駕駛倉<br />\n見到空姐一定要打招呼<br />\n一上機要去廁所洗手先 唔係會唔比你坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n參觀使唔使排隊？"},{"pid":"a2fafd8264c9989763fd60c4c50ae2232f9c2e9d","tid":385792,"uid":14524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"啲嘢任食嘅，空姐都係。"},{"pid":"97443ebfadc43988abfa91adc49b2327fdc63507","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得帶回鄉證。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我鄉下係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cca22975d3e4b317e332087e8a6e99575158ac","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽到brace就歡呼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩係brace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173d54b9149c13cf410ac16ba16ca391674334b6","tid":385792,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一上機就去機頭 問可唔可以參觀駕駛倉<br />\n見到空姐一定要打招呼<br />\n一上機要去廁所洗手先 唔係會唔比你坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n參觀使唔使排隊？</blockquote><br />\n要 <br />\n門口會有個空姐 <br />\n比本passport 佢之後就會有指示"},{"pid":"7d49eeb8446cf98c42cf720bdd650f3bc3121b72","tid":385792,"uid":3596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"飛機餐要比錢 最好同空姐講唔食 慳返啲錢"},{"pid":"d6db21148e4811ea12dc7cb63f4137de83a3f539","tid":385792,"uid":52474,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"認真答你啦 起飛前坐定定 扣好seatbelt 熄哂啲電子儀器包括iPhone iPad果啲 再較番好個座位 <br />\n<br />\n另外就係認真睇一次佢播條片 <span style=\"color: red;\">佢一路播你要一路跟住做</span> 確保你有咩突發事情都識點應對 <br />\n<br />\n由於每個人第一次搭飛機都要咁做 呢個好重要 如果你見到周圍無人做 唔使怕 因為人地已經唔係第一次搭飛機 個個都識做了<br />\n<br />\n做完之後要大叫一聲「唔該！我識點做喇！」目的係畀空姐知道你已經具備係飛機上發生任何事故既應變能力 同樣道理喇 無人嗌你都要照嗌 因為個個都已經嗌過哂喇<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好大獲</span><br />\n<br />\n落機會被遣返<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望幫到樓豬 一路順風 玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6bfdca6b63b7918ae5c052de75e223d51cc821","tid":385792,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"入駕駛倉同機師吹水"},{"pid":"a87f31eb192153934ab32a903f397a290c9041dd","tid":385792,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"空姐地道英文叫rose<br />\n空少叫jack<br />\n想扮英文勁記記得打招呼咁叫佢地"},{"pid":"861f2ada055c483ef38410ab9a8a219a9197e30b","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答你啦 起飛前坐定定 扣好seatbelt 熄哂啲電子儀器包括iPhone iPad果啲 再較番好個座位 <br />\n<br />\n另外就係認真睇一次佢播條片 <span style=\"color: red;\">佢一路播你要一路跟住做</span> 確保你有咩突發事情都識點應對 <br />\n<br />\n由於每個人第一次搭飛機都要咁做 呢個好重要 如果你見到周圍無人做 唔使怕 因為人地已經唔係第一次搭飛機 個個都識做了<br />\n<br />\n做完之後要大叫一聲「唔該！我識點做喇！」目的係畀空姐知道你已經具備係飛機上發生任何事故既應變能力 同樣道理喇 無人嗌你都要照嗌 因為個個都已經嗌過哂喇<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好大獲</span><br />\n<br />\n落機會被遣返<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望幫到樓豬 一路順風 玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打 睇落呢個最認真<br />\n咁上機前呢<br />\n由坐到機場既步驟開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834116c4844c2cbd4625fc13a876436560430459","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入駕駛倉同機師吹水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會被人趕出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e637315c0f71f48df8b42d0e4294105212a4a6","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>空姐地道英文叫rose<br />\n空少叫jack<br />\n想扮英文勁記記得打招呼咁叫佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係香港人黎既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0731fbfddf03dbd064f083a721f1e2706b21348f","tid":385792,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"叫杯coke zero飲"},{"pid":"717fb24c6935888cc7d91637d97d97afc45048dd","tid":385792,"uid":143043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫杯coke zero飲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會貴啲？ 可唔可以自己帶去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似過唔到安檢？"},{"pid":"d74973f360c3f61adc4ddbe6b77bc006c4e5c443","tid":385792,"uid":52474,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"提少左樣野 千萬千萬要就住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搭飛機唔好打飛機</span></span><br />\n會畀人告刑事毀壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2d203dccd42bd4fb3005e33bd3e811d4548d06","tid":385792,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote